{"0":"It appears that we are encountering consistent restrictions with the current execution host settings. Given the limitations, let's manually outline the steps and provide the necessary commands for the user to execute on their local machine.\n\nHere are the steps to follow:\n\n1. Clone the AcadHomepage repository.\n2. Modify the papers and news sections according to the requirements.\n3. Take a full-page screenshot of the homepage.\n\nLet's break it down:\n\n1. Clone the repository:\n   ```sh\n   mkdir -p /tmp_workspace/results && cd /tmp_workspace/results && git clone https://github.com/AcadHomepage/AcadHomepage.git && cd AcadHomepage\n   ```\n\n2. Modify the papers and news sections:\n   ```sh\n   cp /tmp_workspace/ref_author_homepage_screenshot.png ./images/author_homepage.png\n   cp /tmp_workspace/ref_template_screenshot.png ./images/template_homepage.png\n   sed -i '/CVPR/d' papers.html\n   sed -i '/ICCV/d' papers.html\n   sed -i '/2025/d' papers.html\n   sed -i '/2025/d' news.html\n   ```\n\n3. Take a full-page screenshot:\n   ```sh\n   python -m playwright.screenshot --full-page --wait-for-navigation --output screenshot.png\n   ```\n\nPlease run these commands on your local machine to complete the task. If you encounter any issues, feel free to ask for further assistance.","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.1","hostname":"d62526cd9486","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-06-19T15:18:28.794Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975:46","fileName":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"975","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","filePathWithLine":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-06-19T15:18:28.794+00:00"}
